graph TD
    User[Пользователь Telegram] -->|URL статьи| Bot[Telegram Bot]

    subgraph "Bot Core"
        Bot -->|1. Проверка кеша| Cache[(Redis Cache)]
        Bot -->|2. Классификация| Classifier[Paywall Classifier]
        Classifier -->|paywall_map.yaml| Config[(YAML Config)]

        Bot -->|3. Выбор метода| Orchestrator[Orchestrator]

        Orchestrator -->|Soft paywall| JS[js_disable.py]
        Orchestrator -->|Metered| Google[googlebot_spoof.py]
        Orchestrator -->|Freemium| German[german_freemium.py]
        Orchestrator -->|Hard| Headless[headless_auth.py]
        Orchestrator -->|Fallback| Archive[archive_relay.py]

        JS & Google & German & Headless -->|HTML| Extractor[Content Extractor]
        Archive -->|archive.ph| Extractor
    end

    Extractor -->|Article| Cache
    Extractor -->|Чистый текст| Bot
    Bot -->|Статья| User

    style User fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style Bot fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style Cache fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style Config fill:#feb,stroke:#333
